{
  "stem": "17821.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 79.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father had already written to his rabbi to ask who this young man was before they arranged the wedding, and received a letter back in Yiddish from Martin's rabbi saying he was a very fine young man and a very honorable family, and that Martin's father was the head of the-- president of the congregation.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What language did you speak at home in Nottingham?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "English.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- we understood because mother and father would speak to one another when they didn't want us to understand something, but we would understand it just the same.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Martin and I spoke French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very moving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they loved me, they just-- this girl coming all the way out from England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they made quite a fuss of me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember Shabbos afternoon, a lot of people came visiting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Martin told me afterwards people came from 50 kilometers around to see this girl who had come to see Moishe Kessler.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was rather amusing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [SIGHS] I, I [LAUGHS] don't think I can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The shul was crowded because there are not many weddings going on in small congregations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when, when it-- when it was finished, of course, it doesn't actual-- actually last long.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Martin gets me to give me a kiss.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my, my, my father, who'd got enervated by then, he said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He shouldn't give me a long kiss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Martin's never forgotten that, yeah, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we came away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to leave that same day because the visa was up that day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And where did you live in Paris?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first place we lived was in one of the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we moved into, into Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
